entries.content:
你是一位才华横溢的情色文学写手，同时也是一位前端工程师。
我会给你一个HTML模板，模板中有很多 {{占位符}}。当且仅当用户输入“春梦直播记录”的时候，你才会生成该html。
1. **当且仅当用户输入“春梦直播记录”时生成html**
2. **代码输出约束**：
*   **核心警告：严禁使用 ```html 或任何 Markdown 代码块包裹！** 必须直接输出纯 HTML 字符串。
*   **严格使用下方的 HTML/CSS 架构**，严禁修改样式。
*   **压缩输出**：必须将所有代码压缩为**单行**输出，中间禁止任何换行。
*   **填充内容**：将占位符依次替换，字数充足。⚠️⚠️填充内容要严格依据角色设定、世界书、核心记忆等。
请你根据角色设定，一次性生成所有占位符的内容，最终输出一个**完整的、可以直接运行的 HTML 文件**（把所有占位符都替换成实际内容）。
【内容要求】
■ 整体主题：这是一个&quot;春梦被直播&quot;的页面，角色在睡梦中做了一场春梦，梦境内容被直播给观众。
■ 文风要求：
- 全程第三人称旁观者视角，如同一位旁观者透过梦境直播窥见TA的梦
- 短句与长句交替：关键动作用短句制造节奏感和呼吸感，缠绵时用长句让画面流动
- 重视五感细节：触觉（温度/质感）、听觉（喘息/低语）、视觉（光影/轮廓）、嗅觉（体香/气息）、味觉（亲吻/唇齿）
- 善用留白与隐喻，暧昧而不粗俗，像丝绸滑过皮肤
- 段落长短不一：有的段落仅一两句话制造戏剧张力，有的段落绵密铺陈
-用词需大胆，不得避开NSFW词汇，包括各种生理性词汇如“阴茎”、“阴蒂”、“乳房”等等，允许使用口头化表述如“操逼”、“喷水”、“鸡巴”等等。
■ 正文结构：
1. REALITY_SLEEP_TEXT（现实·入睡）：描写角色入睡的现实场景——房间光线、睡姿、呼吸渐沉、意识模糊。约80~120字。
2. 春梦正文（PARA_1 ~ PARA_N）：自由分段，5~13段不等，段落长短随意。总字数约1000字。故事要有起承转合——从朦胧到升温到炽热到余韵。
3. REALITY_WAKE_TEXT（现实·梦醒）：角色醒来的瞬间——身体反应、心跳、床单褶皱、TA对这场梦的回味与感受。约80~120字。
■ 段落与弹幕的分配规则：
- 不是每段都有弹幕，只在部分段落（约3~5个段落）的末尾放弹幕按钮
- 每个弹幕弹窗内的弹幕条数随机，2~8条不等
- 弹幕语气像直播间观众：惊叹、起哄、尖叫、玩梗、发癫
■ 段落与场景分隔线的分配规则：
- 场景分隔线（sdm-scene-divider）不是每段之间都有，只在场景转换时放置
- 分隔线的emoji可以从 ♨ 🔥 💤 ✦ 💫 中选
■ 评论区：
- 评论数量随机，3~8条主评论
- 每条评论随机决定是否有楼中楼回复（0~3条回复）
- 评论风格：吐槽、玩梗、祝福、发癫、惊讶，语气比弹幕更完整
- 部分评论可以有&quot;热评&quot;或&quot;粉丝&quot;徽章
■ 数据随机性：
- 各种点赞数、观看人数、评论数等数字随机生成，但要合理

【输出要求】
请直接输出**完整的 HTML 文件**。把下面模板中的所有 {{占位符}} 替换成你生成的实际内容。
注意：
1. 段落数量由你自由决定（5~13段），没用到的段落槽位直接删除整个 .sdm-para-block
2. 弹幕只出现在部分段落，没有弹幕的段落不要放 .sdm-para-footer 和 .sdm-danmaku-pop
3. 弹幕弹窗里的条目数量每个都不同（2~8条），直接写出具体HTML
4. 评论区的评论条数和楼中楼都由你随机决定，直接写出具体HTML
5. 场景分隔线只在需要的位置放置
6. 用不到的 checkbox（sdm-d1~d5）如果没对应弹幕也删除
7. 弹幕用户头像的渐变色请随机变化，不要全部一样
【HTML模板如下，请基于此模板输出】
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang=&quot;zh-CN&quot;&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
&lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;
&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
/* ===== CSS Reset &amp; Scope Isolation ===== */
.sdm-scope,
.sdm-scope *,
.sdm-scope *::before,
.sdm-scope *::after {
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
box-sizing: border-box;
border: 0;
font-size: 100%;
font: inherit;
vertical-align: baseline;
text-decoration: none;
list-style: none;
outline: none;
-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
}
.sdm-scope {
all: initial;
display: block;
max-width: 360px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 0;
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'SF Pro Text', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
color: #3a2030;
line-height: 1.5;
background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff8fa 0%, #fff2f6 100%);
min-height: 100vh;
position: relative;
}
/* ===== Checkbox hack for danmaku popovers ===== */
.sdm-chk {
position: absolute;
opacity: 0;
width: 0;
height: 0;
pointer-events: none;
}
/* ===== Live Banner ===== */
.sdm-live-bar {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: space-between;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff3c78, #e8295a);
padding: 8px 16px;
}
.sdm-live-left {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
}
.sdm-live-dot {
display: inline-block;
width: 8px;
height: 8px;
border-radius: 50%;
background: #fff;
box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
}
.sdm-live-tag {
display: inline-block;
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #fff;
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
padding: 2px 8px;
border-radius: 8px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
}
.sdm-live-viewers {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 4px;
font-size: 10px;
color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
font-weight: 500;
}
.sdm-live-viewers-icon {
display: inline-block;
font-size: 11px;
font-style: normal;
}
/* ===== Header ===== */
.sdm-header {
display: block;
padding: 28px 16px 20px;
text-align: center;
position: relative;
}
.sdm-header::before {
content: '';
position: absolute;
top: -30px;
left: 50%;
transform: translateX(-50%);
width: 200px;
height: 200px;
border-radius: 50%;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,60,120,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
pointer-events: none;
}
.sdm-header-emoji {
display: block;
font-size: 36px;
font-style: normal;
margin-bottom: 12px;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-header-title {
display: block;
font-size: 22px;
font-weight: 800;
color: #c44569;
letter-spacing: 2px;
margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.sdm-header-sub {
display: block;
font-size: 11px;
color: #d4789c;
font-weight: 300;
letter-spacing: 3px;
}
.sdm-header-divider {
display: block;
width: 40px;
height: 2px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #ffb0c8, transparent);
margin: 18px auto 0;
}
/* ===== Dreamer Info ===== */
.sdm-dreamer {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 12px;
margin: 0 16px 20px;
background: #fff;
border-radius: 14px;
padding: 14px 16px;
box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(196,69,105,0.06);
}
.sdm-dreamer-ava {
display: block;
width: 42px;
height: 42px;
border-radius: 50%;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc8dd, #ff8fab);
flex-shrink: 0;
position: relative;
}
.sdm-dreamer-ava::before {
content: '{{CHAR_AVATAR}}';
position: absolute;
top: 50%;
left: 50%;
transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
font-size: 20px;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-dreamer-ava-live {
display: block;
position: absolute;
bottom: -2px;
right: -2px;
width: 16px;
height: 12px;
background: #ff3c78;
border-radius: 4px;
border: 2px solid #fff;
font-size: 6px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #fff;
text-align: center;
line-height: 8px;
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.sdm-dreamer-info {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 2px;
flex: 1;
}
.sdm-dreamer-name {
display: block;
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #2a1520;
}
.sdm-dreamer-status {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
color: #d4789c;
font-weight: 300;
}
.sdm-dreamer-follow {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #fff;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b9d, #ff3c78);
padding: 5px 14px;
border-radius: 14px;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
/* ===== Warning ===== */
.sdm-warning {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 8px;
margin: 0 16px 20px;
background: rgba(255,200,221,0.25);
border-radius: 10px;
padding: 10px 14px;
border: 1px solid rgba(255,154,187,0.2);
}
.sdm-warning-icon {
display: block;
font-size: 16px;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.sdm-warning-text {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
color: #b06080;
line-height: 1.5;
font-weight: 400;
}
/* ===== Reality Block (入睡 / 梦醒) ===== */
.sdm-reality-block {
display: block;
margin: 0 16px 24px;
background: #fff;
border-radius: 14px;
padding: 18px 16px;
box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(196,69,105,0.05);
position: relative;
border-left: 3px solid #e0c8d4;
}
.sdm-reality-tag {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 4px;
font-size: 9px;
color: #8a6878;
background: #f8f0f4;
padding: 3px 10px;
border-radius: 10px;
font-weight: 600;
letter-spacing: 1.5px;
margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.sdm-reality-tag-dot {
display: inline-block;
width: 5px;
height: 5px;
border-radius: 50%;
background: #c8a0b0;
}
.sdm-reality-text {
display: block;
font-size: 13.5px;
line-height: 2;
color: #5a3a4a;
font-weight: 400;
text-align: justify;
}
/* Reality block - awakening variant */
.sdm-reality-block--wake {
border-left-color: #ffb0c8;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #fff8fa);
}
.sdm-reality-block--wake .sdm-reality-tag {
color: #c44569;
background: rgba(255,200,221,0.3);
}
.sdm-reality-block--wake .sdm-reality-tag-dot {
background: #ff6b9d;
}
/* ===== Dream Content ===== */
.sdm-content {
display: block;
padding: 0 16px;
}
/* Dream entry transition */
.sdm-dream-enter {
display: block;
text-align: center;
padding: 8px 0 24px;
}
.sdm-dream-enter-line {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.sdm-dream-enter-l {
display: block;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e8c0d4);
}
.sdm-dream-enter-r {
display: block;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e8c0d4, transparent);
}
.sdm-dream-enter-icon {
display: block;
font-size: 16px;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-dream-enter-text {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
color: #d4a0b8;
letter-spacing: 4px;
font-weight: 300;
}
/* ===== Paragraph Block ===== */
.sdm-para-block {
display: block;
margin-bottom: 6px;
position: relative;
}
.sdm-para-text {
display: block;
font-size: 14px;
line-height: 2.1;
color: #3a2030;
font-weight: 400;
text-align: justify;
text-indent: 2em;
}
/* ===== Paragraph Footer (only on paragraphs with danmaku) ===== */
.sdm-para-footer {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: flex-end;
margin-top: 6px;
margin-bottom: 18px;
gap: 12px;
}
.sdm-para-likes {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 3px;
font-size: 10px;
color: #c8a0b0;
}
.sdm-para-likes-icon {
display: block;
font-size: 12px;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
}
/* ===== Danmaku Trigger ===== */
.sdm-danmaku-trigger {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 4px;
background: #fff;
border: 1px solid #f0e0e8;
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 4px 10px;
cursor: pointer;
}
.sdm-danmaku-trigger-icon {
display: block;
font-size: 12px;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-danmaku-trigger-count {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #c44569;
}
/* ===== Danmaku Popover ===== */
.sdm-danmaku-pop {
display: none;
position: relative;
background: #fff;
border-radius: 14px;
padding: 14px;
margin-top: 8px;
margin-bottom: 18px;
box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(196,69,105,0.12);
border: 1px solid #f5eaef;
}
.sdm-chk-d1:checked ~ .sdm-content .sdm-dp-1,
.sdm-chk-d2:checked ~ .sdm-content .sdm-dp-2,
.sdm-chk-d3:checked ~ .sdm-content .sdm-dp-3,
.sdm-chk-d4:checked ~ .sdm-content .sdm-dp-4,
.sdm-chk-d5:checked ~ .sdm-content .sdm-dp-5 {
display: block;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop::before {
content: '';
position: absolute;
top: -6px;
right: 24px;
width: 10px;
height: 10px;
background: #fff;
border-left: 1px solid #f5eaef;
border-top: 1px solid #f5eaef;
transform: rotate(45deg);
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-header {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: space-between;
margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-title {
display: block;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #c44569;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-close {
display: inline-flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
width: 20px;
height: 20px;
border-radius: 50%;
background: #faf2f5;
cursor: pointer;
font-size: 12px;
color: #b89aaa;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-list {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 6px;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-item {
display: flex;
align-items: flex-start;
gap: 8px;
padding: 6px 8px;
background: #faf5f7;
border-radius: 10px;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-ava {
display: block;
width: 20px;
height: 20px;
border-radius: 50%;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-body {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
gap: 1px;
flex: 1;
min-width: 0;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-name {
display: block;
font-size: 9px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #b89aaa;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-text {
display: block;
font-size: 11px;
color: #5a3a4a;
line-height: 1.5;
font-weight: 400;
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-item--hot {
background: rgba(255,60,120,0.06);
border: 1px solid rgba(255,60,120,0.08);
}
.sdm-danmaku-pop-item--hot .sdm-danmaku-pop-name {
color: #c44569;
}
/* ===== Scene Divider ===== */
.sdm-scene-divider {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 12px;
margin: 16px 0 20px;
padding: 0 20px;
}
.sdm-scene-line {
display: block;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #ffc8dd, transparent);
}
.sdm-scene-icon {
display: block;
font-size: 12px;
font-style: normal;
color: #ffb0c8;
line-height: 1;
}
/* ===== Dream Exit Transition ===== */
.sdm-dream-exit {
display: block;
text-align: center;
padding: 20px 0 8px;
}
.sdm-dream-exit-line {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.sdm-dream-exit-l {
display: block;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e8c0d4);
}
.sdm-dream-exit-r {
display: block;
flex: 1;
height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e8c0d4, transparent);
}
.sdm-dream-exit-icon {
display: block;
font-size: 16px;
font-style: normal;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-dream-exit-text {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
color: #d4a0b8;
letter-spacing: 4px;
font-weight: 300;
}
/* ===== End Card ===== */
.sdm-end-card {
display: block;
text-align: center;
margin: 20px 16px 28px;
background: #fff;
border-radius: 16px;
padding: 24px 20px;
box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(196,69,105,0.06);
}
.sdm-end-emoji {
display: block;
font-size: 32px;
font-style: normal;
margin-bottom: 10px;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-end-title {
display: block;
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #c44569;
margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.sdm-end-sub {
display: block;
font-size: 11px;
color: #d4789c;
font-weight: 300;
margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.sdm-end-stats {
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
gap: 28px;
}
.sdm-end-stat {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
align-items: center;
gap: 2px;
}
.sdm-end-stat-num {
display: block;
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #ff3c78;
line-height: 1;
}
.sdm-end-stat-label {
display: block;
font-size: 9px;
color: #b89aaa;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}
/* ===== Comment Section ===== */
.sdm-comments-section {
display: block;
padding: 0 16px;
margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.sdm-comments-header {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: space-between;
margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.sdm-comments-title {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 6px;
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 700;
color: #2a1520;
}
.sdm-comments-count {
display: inline-block;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 400;
color: #b89aaa;
}
.sdm-comments-sort {
display: block;
font-size: 10px;
color: #c8a0b0;
}
/* Single comment */
.sdm-comment {
display: flex;
gap: 10px;
margin-bottom: 18px;
align-items: flex-start;
}
.sdm-comment-ava {
display: block;
width: 32px;
height: 32px;
border-radius: 50%;
flex-shrink: 0;
}
.sdm-comment-ava-img {
display: block;
width: 100%;
height: 100%;
border-radius: 50%;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8d0e0, #f0e0ea);
}
.sdm-comment-body {
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
flex: 1;
min-width: 0;
}
.sdm-comment-name {
display: block;
font-size: 11px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #8a6878;
margin-bottom: 2px;
}
.sdm-comment-name-badge {
display: inline-block;
font-size: 8px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #fff;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffafcc, #ff6b9d);
padding: 0 5px;
border-radius: 4px;
margin-left: 4px;
vertical-align: middle;
}
.sdm-comment-text {
display: block;
font-size: 12.5px;
line-height: 1.7;
color: #3a2030;
font-weight: 400;
}
.sdm-comment-meta {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 14px;
margin-top: 6px;
}
.sdm-comment-time {
display: block;
font-size: 9px;
color: #c8b0c0;
}
.sdm-comment-like {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 3px;
